= Equipment System =

This page provides detailed equipment statistics for Dragon Warrior IV (NES), including attack/defense values, prices, and character equip restrictions.

== ROM Data Structure ==

Equipment data is stored across multiple tables in the ROM:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Data Type !! ROM Address !! Bank !! Size !! Format
|-
| Weapon Attack || $0a010 || 5 (PRG $02) || $24 bytes || 1 byte per weapon
|-
| Armor Defense || $0a034 || 5 (PRG $02) || $19 bytes || 1 byte per armor
|-
| Shield Defense || $0a04d || 5 (PRG $02) || $0b bytes || 1 byte per shield
|-
| Helmet Defense || $0a058 || 5 (PRG $02) || $09 bytes || 1 byte per helmet
|-
| Item Prices || $08010 || 4 (PRG $02) || $100 || 2 bytes per item (LE)
|-
| Equip Restrictions || $0a100 || 5 (PRG $02) || $80 || Bitmask per item
|}

