== Damage Formulas ==

=== Physical Damage ===

<nowiki>
Base Damage = (Attack Power - Target Defense/2)
Variation = ±12.5%
Final Damage = Base Damage × Variation × Modifiers
</nowiki>

=== Attack Power Calculation ===

<nowiki>
Attack Power = Character Strength + Weapon Attack + Bonus Modifiers
</nowiki>

=== Defense Calculation ===

<nowiki>
Total Defense = Character Vitality + Armor DEF + Shield DEF + Helmet DEF
</nowiki>

